50 years ago, mankind rose once again to conquer the skies. After 1000 years of barred wastelands, humans have once again found the technology that allowed the past civilization to live in the skies. Soon after, many others started using this technology to travel and trade among them. However, this lead to conflicts with the already established civilization on the ground. Soon enough, segregation conquered the minds of man again. With both forces preparing for total war, Alexander, a pirate, decided to take interest in this war. However, treachery took hold in his ship, and it is up to him to rightfully take what's his, no matter who stands in his way. 